– You're under arrest! You're under arrest!

262
00:09:10.030 --> 00:09:12.530
Looks like I'll have to stamp out these sparks...

263
00:09:12.990 --> 00:09:16.290
before they flare up!

264
00:09:16.290 --> 00:09:17.870
...play your roles!

265
00:09:20.040 --> 00:09:22.210
Listen, everyone.

266
00:09:22.210 --> 00:09:23.580
You're in Wano now.

267
00:09:24.130 --> 00:09:26.130
The shogun of this land is...

268
00:09:26.130 --> 00:09:28.760
Kurozumi Orochi!

269
00:09:30.090 --> 00:09:36.390
All of his officials are under
the control of Kaido.

270
00:09:36.390 --> 00:09:40.310
That's what makes them all so high-handed.

271
00:09:41.060 --> 00:09:45.820
Therefore, if you even touch them,
Kaido will hear about it!

272
00:09:46.190 --> 00:09:50.610
Until all of our allies get here
and we're ready to fight,

273
00:09:51.110 --> 00:09:54.450
we cannot afford to be discovered!

274
00:09:54.950 --> 00:09:58.160
So you must all pretend
to be regular citizens for now...

275
00:09:58.540 --> 00:10:01.710
and quietly—I repeat, quietly—

276
00:10:01.710 --> 00:10:05.750
play your roles!

277
00:10:08.920 --> 00:10:10.710
I guess I have no choice...

278
00:10:10.710 --> 00:10:12.090
I got it...

279
00:10:12.090 --> 00:10:13.760
verily...

280
00:10:13.760 --> 00:10:15.180
Hey, tie him up!

281
00:10:15.180 --> 00:10:18.930
– You're under arrest! You're under arrest!
– You're under arrest! You're under arrest!

282
00:10:25.440 --> 00:10:29.780
It's the arch rogue who's been
terrorizing our streets!

283
00:10:29.780 --> 00:10:33.860
The magistrate has finally,
finally captured him!

284
00:10:33.860 --> 00:10:36.740
The criminal has been sentenced to seppuku!

285
00:10:36.740 --> 00:10:39.410
You can get all the details in here!

286
00:10:39.410 --> 00:10:41.450
I hate his guts!

287
00:10:41.450 --> 00:10:44.290
He turned his blade against my husband too!

288
00:10:44.290 --> 00:10:46.130
What a relief!

289
00:10:46.130 --> 00:10:50.250
Just this month, he slashed
three people on the streets at night.

290
00:10:53.880 --> 00:10:56.970
Hey, can I have one, too?!

291
00:10:56.970 --> 00:10:58.180
Thank you!

292
00:10:59.350 --> 00:11:02.520
Z-Zorojuro...
"The Slasher, Zorojuro"

293
00:11:10.610 --> 00:11:14.030
So your name is Zorojuro...

294
00:11:15.110 --> 00:11:19.490
Everyone was fearful of the slasher...

295
00:11:19.490 --> 00:11:24.120
If you slash your belly,
the town will become peaceful again.

296
00:11:26.080 --> 00:11:29.250
And I can hardly believe...

297
00:11:29.790 --> 00:11:33.010
you're also a grave robber.

298
00:11:33.670 --> 00:11:35.880
Twenty-three years ago...

299
00:11:36.430 --> 00:11:39.800
amid the confusion of a pirate incident...

300
00:11:39.800 --> 00:11:43.520
the corpse of the legendary swordsman Ryuma went missing...

301
00:11:44.180 --> 00:11:46.440
along with his named blade Shusui!

302
00:11:47.730 --> 00:11:52.690
Legend has it that Ryuma sliced off
the head of a giant, savage dragon...

303
00:11:53.190 --> 00:11:56.700
with this very sword, Shusui.

304
00:11:58.990 --> 00:12:02.370
Although, slasher...

305
00:12:02.990 --> 00:12:06.580
That grave robbery took place
twenty-three years ago.

306
00:12:06.960 --> 00:12:09.540
You don't look that old.

307
00:12:10.040 --> 00:12:12.290
Did you steal it from the original thief?

308
00:12:15.340 --> 00:12:16.970
Oh, well...

309
00:12:16.970 --> 00:12:21.390
The famous Shusui is now in my hands!

310
00:12:26.680 --> 00:12:27.940
Yes, sir.

311
00:12:27.940 --> 00:12:31.310
Now, Zorojuro, it's time.

312
00:12:35.690 --> 00:12:36.740
Hey.

313
00:12:37.240 --> 00:12:39.530
This blade has no grip...

314
00:12:42.870 --> 00:12:44.160
verily.

315
00:12:44.160 --> 00:12:48.540
A seppuku blade is usually short
and has no grip.

316
00:12:48.540 --> 00:12:52.170
It's not meant for combat after all.

317
00:12:52.170 --> 00:12:56.590
Do you know the proper etiquette of seppuku?

318
00:12:57.170 --> 00:13:02.510
If you call yourself a samurai,
admit your guilt and kill yourself honorably!

319
00:13:02.850 --> 00:13:05.600
Before you start suffering...

320
00:13:06.720 --> 00:13:09.020
I'll assist in your death!

321
00:13:28.620 --> 00:13:30.330
Well then...

322
00:13:30.330 --> 00:13:31.460
So long.

323
00:13:34.540 --> 00:13:36.840
Just don't cry like a baby...

324
00:13:37.460 --> 00:13:42.050
A proper death is a samurai's honor.

325
00:13:42.590 --> 00:13:44.640
We have witnesses!

326
00:13:44.640 --> 00:13:46.390
And enough evidence!

327
00:13:46.970 --> 00:13:50.600
This will be an honorable death
that you don't deserve!

328
00:13:51.560 --> 00:13:54.520
Be happy that you can perform seppuku.

329
00:14:10.790 --> 00:14:13.330
I smell blood.

330
00:14:16.920 --> 00:14:18.300
You...

331
00:14:19.880 --> 00:14:21.380
are the culprit!

332
00:14:49.120 --> 00:14:52.580
I'm sorry, Kin'emon.

333
00:15:13.100 --> 00:15:15.520
Ouch!

334
00:15:31.370 --> 00:15:34.330
Is this... Wano?

335
00:15:51.310 --> 00:15:53.640
Where did everyone go?

336
00:15:54.680 --> 00:15:56.600
Let's see...

337
00:15:57.350 --> 00:16:00.560
What happened to us?

338
00:16:17.580 --> 00:16:18.330
Hey!

339
00:16:22.170 --> 00:16:23.210
Hey, you!

340
00:16:23.210 --> 00:16:25.710
Don't break our ship!

341
00:16:27.340 --> 00:16:28.930
It's a giant dog!

342
00:16:31.970 --> 00:16:34.640
Is it a dog or a boar?

343
00:16:51.950 --> 00:16:51.990
A Baboon

344
00:16:51.990 --> 00:16:54.910
A Baboon

345
00:17:00.670 --> 00:17:02.920
An animal with a sword?

346
00:17:02.920 --> 00:17:05.670
I guess that's just how Wano is!

347
00:17:12.680 --> 00:17:17.390
The first thing I see here is
a fight between two wild beasts?

348
00:17:45.340 --> 00:17:47.090
Listen, guys!

349
00:17:47.090 --> 00:17:50.380
You can fight all you want
but don't damage the ship!

350
00:17:56.050 --> 00:17:57.390
Oh, yeah...

351
00:18:00.020 --> 00:18:02.480
What was I doing?

352
00:18:07.940 --> 00:18:11.990
After we climbed up
the waterfall, we saw land...

353
00:18:11.990 --> 00:18:15.820
But we were sucked into a whirlpool
before getting there...

354
00:18:15.820 --> 00:18:17.530
What's this?!

355
00:18:17.530 --> 00:18:20.160
Hey, the tide is running in reverse!

356
00:18:21.620 --> 00:18:23.210
Hang in there, Sunny!

357
00:18:25.830 --> 00:18:28.090
Nami, hold onto me!

358
00:18:28.090 --> 00:18:29.920
Thank you, Sanji!

359
00:18:29.920 --> 00:18:32.550
You're most welcome, Nami!

360
00:18:32.550 --> 00:18:33.840
Sanji!

361
00:18:33.840 --> 00:18:35.260
Yeah, hold onto me!

362
00:18:35.260 --> 00:18:37.930
Okay, I'm gonna jump to land!

363
00:18:39.720 --> 00:18:40.720
Ready?!

364
00:18:40.720 --> 00:18:42.520
Wait, Sanji!

365
00:18:44.520 --> 00:18:47.360
Take me with you!

366
00:18:47.360 --> 00:18:48.860
Chobro!

367
00:18:48.860 --> 00:18:50.360
I can't! Too heavy!

368
00:18:50.360 --> 00:18:53.780
No! Don't leave me behind!

369
00:18:54.240 --> 00:18:56.240
I'm sorry, but you need to let go.

370
00:18:57.490 --> 00:18:59.990
How could you...?!

371
00:19:00.450 --> 00:19:01.790
Just kidding.

372
00:19:01.790 --> 00:19:03.330
Hold on tightly!

373
00:19:03.330 --> 00:19:04.750
Sanji!

374
00:19:07.040 --> 00:19:09.750
Then allow me to join, too.

375
00:19:10.880 --> 00:19:12.510
I love you all!

376
00:19:12.510 --> 00:19:14.380
Squeeze!

377
00:19:14.720 --> 00:19:16.970
Those are some hard bones!

378
00:19:16.970 --> 00:19:19.810
Not bones! Bones are so creepy!

379
00:19:20.220 --> 00:19:22.310
Use my belly, Sanji!

380
00:19:24.690 --> 00:19:26.020
Okay!

381
00:19:30.440 --> 00:19:31.650
See you later!

382
00:19:31.650 --> 00:19:34.240
Yeah, I'm right behind you!

383
00:19:37.610 --> 00:19:39.870
Alright, it's my turn to go!

384
00:19:39.870 --> 00:19:42.910
Sunny! I promise I'll find you later!

385
00:19:48.880 --> 00:19:51.340
Here I go!

386
00:19:54.170 --> 00:19:56.050
The octopus?!

387
00:19:56.630 --> 00:20:00.720
What do you still want from me?!

388
00:20:00.720 --> 00:20:04.730
Damn octopus!

389
00:20:17.900 --> 00:20:20.990
Then, I was here when I woke up.

390
00:20:21.700 --> 00:20:24.700
So am I above the waterfall? Or did I fall?

391
00:20:24.700 --> 00:20:27.620
Did I make it to Wano?

392
00:20:34.880 --> 00:20:35.760
Oh?

393
00:20:35.760 --> 00:20:37.300
The vivre card is gone!

394
00:20:38.760 --> 00:20:40.430
I lost it!

395
00:20:40.430 --> 00:20:42.010
Is it in the sea?!

396
00:20:42.600 --> 00:20:44.890
Damn!

397
00:20:48.270 --> 00:20:49.520
Oh, well!

398
00:20:49.520 --> 00:20:50.480
Forget it.

399
00:20:50.480 --> 00:20:52.560
Stop!

400
00:20:52.560 --> 00:20:57.320
Let me go! I didn't say anything like that!

401
00:20:57.320 --> 00:20:59.860
Give me back my rice, too!

402
00:21:00.280 --> 00:21:02.490
No, I'm sure you said it!

403
00:21:03.160 --> 00:21:08.250
When the Kozuki Clan comes back,
they'll teach you a lesson!

404
00:21:08.250 --> 00:21:09.870
You traitor...

405
00:21:11.170 --> 00:21:15.090
You're an ally of that evil
family, the Kozuki Clan!

406
00:21:15.090 --> 00:21:16.920
It's a serious crime!

407
00:21:16.920 --> 00:21:19.800
We'll either sell you to a brothel
or send you to prison.

408
00:21:19.800 --> 00:21:20.880
There'll be no mercy!

409
00:21:21.470 --> 00:21:22.640
But...!

410
00:21:22.640 --> 00:21:24.390
Pipe down for a second.

411
00:21:24.810 --> 00:21:26.770
We're on duty now!

412
00:21:29.560 --> 00:21:31.390
Look! There's a ship on the beach!

413
00:21:31.390 --> 00:21:33.480
Just one survivor?

414
00:21:33.480 --> 00:21:36.570
And our baboon's having
trouble with that lion-dog!

415
00:21:36.570 --> 00:21:38.990
He's not so dependable as a guard, huh?

416
00:21:40.490 --> 00:21:42.160
Oh! Komachiyo?!

417
00:21:45.740 --> 00:21:48.120
Guys, that's enough...

418
00:21:48.120 --> 00:21:50.790
Boss! Looks like the report was right!

419
00:21:50.790 --> 00:21:52.420
It's the trespassing ship!

420
00:21:52.830 --> 00:21:54.250
Do you see its crew?

421
00:21:54.250 --> 00:21:55.540
There's just one.

422
00:21:55.920 --> 00:21:57.300
One, huh?

423
00:21:57.300 --> 00:22:00.050
We'll knock him out and take him with us!

424
00:22:00.050 --> 00:22:02.630
He'll at least become our laborer!

425
00:22:07.930 --> 00:22:10.310
Good boy. Sleep well!

426
00:22:11.690 --> 00:22:16.230
When you wake up, we'll treat
you so well as our slave!

427
00:22:31.540 --> 00:22:32.460
What the...?!

428
00:22:37.840 --> 00:22:39.630
Attacking me all of a sudden?

429
00:22:39.630 --> 00:22:41.170
You bastard!

430
00:22:46.010 --> 00:22:47.720
I can't hit him!

431
00:22:48.720 --> 00:22:50.720
Hey, what's going on?

432
00:22:50.720 --> 00:22:52.560
Well, it's nothing...

433
00:23:09.080 --> 00:23:11.790
This beach is so rowdy.

434
00:23:12.250 --> 00:23:13.660
Dammit...

435
00:23:14.290 --> 00:23:15.920
Hey, baboon!

436
00:23:15.920 --> 00:23:18.840
Don't just stand there and watch!

437
00:23:19.210 --> 00:23:20.920
You can get the lion-dog later!

438
00:23:20.920 --> 00:23:22.510
Catch that guy!

439
00:23:27.510 --> 00:23:29.850
Actually, you now have permission...

440
00:23:29.850 --> 00:23:31.350
to kill him!

441
00:24:02.920 --> 00:24:04.340
What do you want?

442
00:24:34.200 --> 00:24:35.160
Good!

443
00:24:35.160 --> 00:24:38.290
Don't fight so much, guys!

444
00:24:41.380 --> 00:24:44.130
What the hell are you afraid of?!

445
00:24:44.130 --> 00:24:46.720
He's just a lousy pirate!

446
00:25:00.440 --> 00:25:04.610
Look what you did, you squirt!

447
00:25:05.190 --> 00:25:07.240
I'll kill you!

448
00:25:08.320 --> 00:25:10.700
Stop right there, you damn brat!

449
00:25:10.700 --> 00:25:12.530
F-Forgive me!

450
00:25:19.830 --> 00:25:21.210
I surrender!

451
00:25:21.540 --> 00:25:23.170
I surrender!

452
00:25:24.460 --> 00:25:26.670
What are you doing?

453
00:25:26.670 --> 00:25:29.050
I said I surrender!

454
00:25:29.050 --> 00:25:31.430
I surrender!

455
00:25:31.680 --> 00:25:31.720
Otama

456
00:25:31.720 --> 00:25:35.010
Otama

457
00:25:36.010 --> 00:25:38.350
I'm not gonna do anything to you!

458
00:25:38.350 --> 00:25:41.310
Y-You mean it?

459
00:25:41.730 --> 00:25:43.190
Yeah!

460
00:25:43.190 --> 00:25:45.150
U-Um...

461
00:25:45.650 --> 00:25:50.490
I'm sorry but while you're here,
may I have some of your time?

462
00:25:50.490 --> 00:25:52.160
Th-This is my chance!

463
00:25:53.110 --> 00:25:55.660
Chance? What do you mean?

464
00:25:55.660 --> 00:25:57.370
All right. Let's do it.

465
00:25:57.370 --> 00:25:58.830
Huh? Do what?

466
00:25:59.160 --> 00:26:02.080
Millet Dumpling!

467
00:26:05.340 --> 00:26:07.090
Here we go!

468
00:26:07.090 --> 00:26:08.000
What?!

469
00:26:08.000 --> 00:26:10.010
Your cheek came off!

470
00:26:14.550 --> 00:26:16.260
Go ahead. Eat it.

471
00:26:25.980 --> 00:26:27.940
Wh-What are you doing?

472
00:26:42.460 --> 00:26:43.670
Shake.

473
00:26:48.420 --> 00:26:49.420
What?!

474
00:26:49.420 --> 00:26:52.130
She tamed that beast!

475
00:26:52.130 --> 00:26:53.880
I did it!

476
00:26:54.260 --> 00:26:59.850
I finally befriended
the savage mountain baboon!

477
00:26:59.850 --> 00:27:00.890
Yay!

478
00:27:00.890 --> 00:27:03.020
I did it!

479
00:27:03.020 --> 00:27:05.150
So you're an ability user!

480
00:27:05.150 --> 00:27:07.480
That power's pretty handy!

481
00:27:12.440 --> 00:27:13.610
Okay, okay.

482
00:27:13.610 --> 00:27:15.950
You're our friend now!

483
00:27:18.370 --> 00:27:19.700
Good boy.

484
00:27:19.700 --> 00:27:21.580
Is that your dog?

485
00:27:22.330 --> 00:27:23.750
He is!

486
00:27:23.750 --> 00:27:25.790
I named him Komachiyo!

487
00:27:27.210 --> 00:27:29.340
Oh, Komachiyo!

488
00:27:29.340 --> 00:27:30.460
Nice to meet you!

489
00:27:30.460 --> 00:27:32.460
I'm Luffy!

490
00:27:36.510 --> 00:27:39.010
And my name is Otama.

491
00:27:39.850 --> 00:27:41.760
Okay, Otama!

492
00:27:41.760 --> 00:27:43.180
Nice to meet you, too!

493
00:27:43.180 --> 00:27:44.980
Nice to meet you!

494
00:27:44.980 --> 00:27:45.640
Now...

495
00:27:45.640 --> 00:27:49.860
I need to know if this country is Wano or not.

496
00:27:50.320 --> 00:27:51.980
This country?

497
00:27:53.400 --> 00:27:56.740
Yes, this is Wano!

498
00:27:57.070 --> 00:28:00.950
You're in the Kuri region of Wano...

499
00:28:00.950 --> 00:28:02.330
Big Bro!

500
00:28:02.330 --> 00:28:05.460
So I am in Wano!

501
00:28:06.250 --> 00:28:09.830
I finally made it to Wano!

502
00:28:10.170 --> 00:28:12.550
Wait for me, Kaido!

503
00:28:12.550 --> 00:28:14.210
Wait! "Big Bro"?!

504
00:28:14.630 --> 00:28:15.340
Hey!

505
00:28:15.340 --> 00:28:17.550
Since when am I your big brother?!

506
00:28:18.890 --> 00:28:21.010
A big brother is a big brother!

507
00:28:21.350 --> 00:28:22.850
What does that even mean?

508
00:28:22.850 --> 00:28:24.600
Well, it's no big deal.

509
00:28:24.600 --> 00:28:27.190
Okay, Big Bro!

510
00:28:33.270 --> 00:28:37.030
Communication from Kuri beach
seems to have been cut.

511
00:28:37.030 --> 00:28:40.200
They were probably beaten by someone.

512
00:28:40.570 --> 00:28:42.410
We don't know how many there are.

513
00:28:43.580 --> 00:28:45.700
What should we do, Boss?

514
00:28:55.090 --> 00:28:57.590
Don't tell Kaido.

515
00:29:00.590 --> 00:29:02.430
I'll handle it!
